Bash Scripts for Linux Training

#1 [Under Construction]

Welcome to the Linux and Shell Scripting Training Scripts repository! This collection features a series of bash scripts designed for beginner to advanced Linux users, covering essential skills, commands, and automation tasks. These scripts are crafted to be educational, showcasing best practices and useful techniques to help you master the Linux command line.
Overview

Each script is written to illustrate a particular concept or technique in Linux, whether itâ€™s basic file manipulation, process management, networking commands, or scripting logic. They are organized in a way that encourages self-paced learning, making it easy to understand, modify, and apply in various scenarios.
